* Tables 4 and A.1.  Pre-trend summary and coefficients
*   OLS event-study pre-trend tests (no csdid).
*   Writes pretrend_summary.tex and pretrend_coef.tex to $tabs.
*========================================================================*
*========================================================================*
* Table A.2.  Within-state variation
*   Per-municipality cohort-trend dispersion.
*   Writes within_state_variation.tex to $tabs.
