* Reproduces the existing Output/fixed_analysis/pretrend_coef.tex layout
* with freshly-estimated levels/trends coefficients (manual file write so
* the structure is byte-stable regardless of esttab version).
*------------------------------------------------------------------------*

estimates restore levels
local nL = e(N)
